<h2 class="wikipedia">Wikipedia</h2>
<div class="wikipedia-extract-body wikipedia-extract-collapse"><p><b>Michael Alden Hedges</b> (December 31, 1953 – December 2, 1997) was an American composer, acoustic guitarist and singer-songwriter.</p>
<p></p></div>
<a href="https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Michael_Hedges">Continue reading at Wikipedia...</a>
